(293, 40, 0, 1, '2018-02-14 18:11:09', '2018-02-14 15:27:26', 40, 'en', 1, 1, 'Registration and Startelist', 'Registration and Startelist', NULL, '<p>Dear Runner!<br /> We offer the following races on Saturday 21 April 2018:</p>\n<div class="wpsm-comptable-wrap">\n<table id="wpsm-table-1" class="wpsm-comptable  wpsm-comptable-responsive stacktable large-only">\n<thead class="wpsm-thead wpsm-thead-default">\n<tr><th>Distance</th><th>Starting Time</th><th>Agegroup</th><th>Fee</th></tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class="wpsm-tbody">\n<tr>\n<td class="">circa 10 km FunRun</td>\n<td>19.10 h</td>\n<td>14 and older</td>\n<td>20 GEL / ca. 8 US$ / ca. 7 EUR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="">21,1 km HalfMarathon</td>\n<td>19.30 h</td>\n<td>16 and older</td>\n<td>40 GEL / ca. 16 US$ / ca. 14 EUR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="">1.000 m KidsRun</td>\n<td>18.45 h</td>\n<td>10 &ndash; 13</td>\n<td>Free of Charge</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="">500 m KidsRun</td>\n<td>18.30 h</td>\n<td>6 &ndash; 9</td>\n<td>Free of Charge</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p data-reactid="76">If you register prior to 11 March 2018 you will get a personalized bib number with your first name on.</p>\n<p data-reactid="76">If you are a team, a club, a company or just an enthusiastic group of runners and want to register six or more of your runners, please get in touch with us for a special group registration.</p>\n<p>All runners aged 18 and over can participate in the races. If you are 14 &ndash; 15 years old you can participate in the FunRun, if you are 16 &ndash; 17 years old you can participate in both the FunRun or the halfmarathon. In any case please send us a formless written consent of the legal representative. A membership in a sportsclub or federation is not necessary.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="https://portal.mikatiming.de/event/batumi-nightrace/2018/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong><img class="aligncenter wp-image-345 " src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/REGISTER_NOW-3-300x114.png" alt="" width="339" height="129" /></strong></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong><br /> The online registration closes on Friday 13 April 2018 at 24.00 h. After that date you have the possibility to use the Late Registration. For details please see General Information.</p>\n<p>As you register please do not forget to tick the box for your personal THE GREAT BATUMI NIGHT RACE running shirt. It&rsquo;s free of charge!</p>\n<p>If you are interested in booking your accomodation please get in touch with the <a href="http://colosseummarina.ge/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hotel Colosseum Marina</a>. The hotel offers you as participant of the race attractive deals to spend a great weekend in Batumi.</p>\n<p>Your friends are already registered &hellip; ?! Check out the <a href="https://portal.mikatiming.de/event/batumi-nightrace/2018/starter/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">starterlist</a>.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'registration-and-startelist', NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'registration, startelist, სიცოცხლის, წიგნი', 'Registration and Startelist', 0, NULL),
