(297, 42, 0, 1, '2018-02-14 18:12:03', '2018-02-14 15:27:23', 42, 'en', 1, 1, 'Media', 'Media', NULL, '<p>Dear Media Representatives!</p>\n<p>The organizers of THE GREAT BATUMI NIGHT RACE welcome you very warmly. We are pleased that you are interested in working with us. We appreciate you to issue an official accreditation.</p>\n<p>Please note:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Please send us an E-Mail before 13 April 2018 to apply formally for the official accreditation.</li>\n<li>Please attach a copy of your press card.</li>\n<li>Your official accreditation for THE GREAT BATUMI NIGHT RACE is free of charge.<span id="result_box" class="" lang="en"></span></li>\n<li>We exclusively give those media representatives an accreditation, which report on our event.</li>\n<li>You, as media representatives, have the exclusive right to use the created materials commercially.</li>\n<li><span id="result_box" class="" lang="en"><span class="">We inform you about the completion of your accreditation and ask you to pick it up at the office of the organizer.</span></span></li>\n<li>We will provide you with an identity card, which you must wear permanently during the event and which must be presented at the request of the organizers.<span id="result_box" class="" lang="en"></span></li>\n<li>When you arrive at the venue, please contact the Racedirector.</li>\n<li>Please always behave in such a way that neither runners nor organizers are hindered.</li>\n<li>Please follow the instructions of the organizers and the police.</li>\n<li>Please check with the organizer in advance if you intent to go on a trip on the race course during the entire duration of the event with vehicles of any kind.</li>\n<li><span id="result_box" class="" lang="en"><span class="">We kindly as you to send us a copy, a link or any other record upon completion of your material.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please do not hesitate to contact us for further information.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'media', NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'media, სიცოცხლის, წიგნი', 'Media', 0, NULL),
